{"tid":2188188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度再禁118個中國APP　騰訊《絕地求生》Alipay榜上有名","createTime":"2020-09-04T05:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T14:09:34.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad250179d6b5b40ef83c00dcbdc06173c75f9256","tid":2188188,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200902/F5RRTGMUCVDDFN2HXEECBB4WSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200902%2FF5RRTGMUCVDDFN2HXEECBB4WSQ%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cXobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=0b9fb4fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200902%2FF5RRTGMUCVDDFN2HXEECBB4WSQ%2F&h=9c755b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200902/F5RRTGMUCVDDFN2HXEECBB4WSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n印度電子和信息技術部（MEIT）周三宣佈再禁止118個中國應用程式，包括俗稱「食雞」的騰訊手機遊戲《絕地求生》（PlayerUnknown&rsquo;s Battlegrounds，PUBG）及旗下其他程式、Alipay、AlipayHK、搜尋引擎百度、約會網站，甚至是用於編輯自拍的軟件等。<br />\n<br />\nMEIT在聲明中指，被禁的118個程式推動「危害印度主權與完整、國防、國家安全和公共秩序」活動。《絕地求生》在印度廣受年輕人歡迎，估計玩家達數百萬。<br />\n<br />\n今年6月15日中印兩國在邊境爆發45年來最嚴重的流血衝突，導致至少20名印度軍人死亡。外媒報道，解放軍持狼牙棒突襲，但印度士兵只以拳頭和石頭迎戰，雙方激戰長達7小時，由於衝突地點在陡峭山脊，最終雙方有很多士兵失足墮崖致失救凍死。自此雙方關係轉趨緊張，印度稍後宣佈禁止59個中國程式包括TikTok。<br />\n<br />\n本周日兩國軍隊又再度傳出發生衝突。印度媒體指，數百解放軍越界，闖入班公湖南岸印軍實際控制線內，佔據一處名為「頭盔頂」的山頭，並開始進行相關的防禦工程。而駐守班公湖附近的印軍藏兵，曾因阻止解放軍進行有關工程而與對方爆發肢體衝撞，導致數十名解放軍受傷，但現場並沒有槍擊的報告。"},{"pid":"51478edd578a2e5c1118128456af07168b5630da","tid":2188188,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"反正隻垃圾game咁多外掛狗<br />\nbam咗都係好事嚟"},{"pid":"7b3766c83a93f0f2e0ef102047f2b537afe73fe7","tid":2188188,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"食雞跟本係垃圾game, 冇目的, 臝輸都係不斷咁輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713220dad85c8c0d7e69bafefb8a143aba7b36f4","tid":2188188,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AmardipGupta4/status/1300811400474836992?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmardipGupta4%2Fstatus%2F1300811400474836992%3Fs%3D20&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cXobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=53a93909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmardipGupta4%2Fstatus%2F1300811400474836992%3Fs%3D20&h=33e093b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AmardipGupta4/status/1300811400474836992?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"78612287bb3ad9855da1134bf62c5ddf42da52e2","tid":2188188,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"全世界都應該要學印佬"},{"pid":"4287a724908ee6370fa6205b9a574b82ac77bc2d","tid":2188188,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印度真係好勇"}]}